  <body>
    <segment id="1">

Don&apos;t forget!</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="26" relname="interpretation"> 

Every year again stress before the holidays.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="25" relname="span"> 

On Saturday quite a few people were still rushing from store to store,</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="2" relname="purpose"> to do the last shopping.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="26" relname="span">  

Some people only now seemed to have remembered that they could give something to their loved ones on Christmas Eve.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="22" relname="joint">

But it is not only because of such forgetfulness that many people will again have to do without a gift of love tonight.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="22" relname="joint">

Häufig werden sie über all dem Feiertagstrubel wirklich vergessen , die Alten und Einsamen , die Flüchtlinge und Asylsuchenden, die Heimatlosen, Hungernden, Kranken.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="22" relname="interpretation">

Remembering these losers of our time should not spoil anyone&apos;s Christmas.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="20" relname="preparation">  

On the contrary:</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="20" relname="list"> Perhaps a few thoughts about those who are not so fortunate today will make us even more aware of our own good fortune.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="18" relname="means">

Perhaps such thoughts will also keep you awake ,</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="18" relname="span"> 

so that you don&apos;t miss the opportunity to help,</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="14" relname="condition"> 

when it presents itself.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="16" relname="evaluation-s"> 

Who wants to doubt it:</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="17" relname="span">  

Christmas should be more than fat food and presents.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="24" relname="interpretation">

With this in mind, the MAZ wishes all readers a merry and reflective Christmas.</segment>
<group id="17" type="span" parent="24" relname="summary" />
